<h1 id="about-hall-of-gods">About Hall of Gods</h1>
<p>A mega jackpot machine worthy of its name! Along with Norse Gods and the Midgard Serpent you’re on the hunt for three jackpots in this classic slot machine, Hall of Gods. With a number of jackpot wins with over a million euros, this video slot has become very popular among new as well as experienced casino players. Expanding wilds, Free Spins and Pick &amp; Click bonus games makes this game very entertaining. These special features trigger quite often so you never get bored. Experience Free Spins with Odins ravens and especially the bonus game where you use the Hammer of Thor to pick shields in the chase for the millions.</p>
<h2 id="game-features">Game Features</h2>
<p>Hall of Gods consist of five reels and three rows. The expanding wilds will show up on reel 2-4 and the game also has a Free Spins mode as well as the bonus game where you can win the jackpots.</p>
<h3 id="wild-2">Wild</h3>
<p>On reel 2-4 you have the chance to hit expanding wilds in the shape of the Midgard Serpent. The best part is that it’s possible to get up to three expanding wilds at the same time which almost certainly brings you the big wins. The wilds replace all symbols except Odin’s ravens and Thor’s hammer.</p>
<h3 id="free-spins">Free Spins</h3>
<p>Once you hit at least three of Odin’s ravens you’ll receive 10 Free Spins. If you hit four you’ll get 15 Free Spins and if you hit five you’ll get 20. If you get additional ravens whilst in the Free Spins mode you’ll receive five extra spins. All winnings during Free Spins are multiplied by 3 (except for winnings in the bonus game).</p>
<h3 id="bonus-game">Bonus Game</h3>
<p>When you’re lucky and get three Thor’s hammers you are transported into the bonus game. Whilst in there you get to use Thor’s hammer to break 15 different shields with. Under the shields you’ll find different coin wins or the three different jackpot symbols – Mini, Midi and Mega. Once you hit three of the same coin wins or three of the same jackpot symbol, the bonus game is over and you collect your winnings. The excitement can be almost overwhelming once you have two jackpot symbols showing and still shields left to hit!</p>
